---
/** Always-available combat + Honour reference for second-screen play. */
---

<details class="bg3-quick-ref" id="bg3-quick-ref">
  <summary class="bg3-quick-ref__summary">
    <span class="bg3-quick-ref__title">Combat &amp; Honour cheat sheet</span>
    <span class="bg3-quick-ref__hint">tap to expand</span>
  </summary>

  <div class="bg3-quick-ref__body">
    <section class="bg3-quick-ref__section" aria-labelledby="bg3-honour-heading">
      <h2 id="bg3-honour-heading" class="bg3-quick-ref__heading">Honour survival</h2>
      <ul class="bg3-quick-ref__list">
        <li>One party wipe ends the run — treat every long rest and pull like it matters.</li>
        <li>Reach <strong>character level 5</strong> before Act 1 optional bosses (Owlbear, harpies, etc.).</li>
        <li>Keep <strong>Rolan</strong> and <strong>Barcus</strong> alive — they gate vendors and gear later.</li>
        <li>Enchantment holds do not work on <strong>undead</strong> — use Command, damage, and party tools.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bg3-quick-ref__section" aria-labelledby="bg3-legend-heading">
      <h2 id="bg3-legend-heading" class="bg3-quick-ref__heading">Legend</h2>
      <ul class="bg3-legend">
        <li><span class="bg3-tag bg3-tag--critical">Critical path</span> First Honour clear</li>
        <li><span class="bg3-tag bg3-tag--optional">Optional</span> Stronger, not required</li>
        <li><span class="bg3-tag bg3-tag--skip">Skip default</span> Avoid on first run</li>
        <li><span class="bg3-tag bg3-tag--missable">Missable</span> Permanent loss if missed</li>
        <li><span class="bg3-tag bg3-tag--gate">Level gate</span> Wait until this level</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bg3-quick-ref__section" aria-labelledby="bg3-stats-heading">
      <h2 id="bg3-stats-heading" class="bg3-quick-ref__heading">Level 1 ability scores (you)</h2>
      <p class="bg3-quick-ref__note">Half-Orc · Bard · tap a value to copy</p>
      <dl class="bg3-stat-sheet" data-stat-sheet>
        <div class="bg3-stat-sheet__row">
          <dt>STR</dt>
          <dd><button type="button" class="bg3-copy-value" data-copy="8">8</button></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="bg3-stat-sheet__row bg3-stat-sheet__row--key">
          <dt>DEX</dt>
          <dd><button type="button" class="bg3-copy-value" data-copy="17">17</button></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="bg3-stat-sheet__row">
          <dt>CON</dt>
          <dd><button type="button" class="bg3-copy-value" data-copy="14">14</button></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="bg3-stat-sheet__row">
          <dt>INT</dt>
          <dd><button type="button" class="bg3-copy-value" data-copy="8">8</button></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="bg3-stat-sheet__row">
          <dt>WIS</dt>
          <dd><button type="button" class="bg3-copy-value" data-copy="10">10</button></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="bg3-stat-sheet__row bg3-stat-sheet__row--key">
          <dt>CHA</dt>
          <dd><button type="button" class="bg3-copy-value" data-copy="16">16</button></dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <section class="bg3-quick-ref__section" aria-labelledby="bg3-combat-heading">
      <h2 id="bg3-combat-heading" class="bg3-quick-ref__heading">Your turn (boss fights)</h2>
      <ol class="bg3-combat-loop">
        <li><span class="bg3-combat-loop__step">1</span> Command (<strong>Approach</strong>) to group — or skip if Hold is enough</li>
        <li><span class="bg3-combat-loop__step">2</span> Hold Person / Hold Monster on boss — <em>before</em> damage</li>
        <li><span class="bg3-combat-loop__step">3</span> Attack + Divine Smite + Slashing Flourish on paralyzed targets</li>
        <li><span class="bg3-combat-loop__step">4</span> Shadow Blade or Booming Blade on leftovers</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="bg3-quick-ref__section" aria-labelledby="bg3-prefight-heading">
      <h2 id="bg3-prefight-heading" class="bg3-quick-ref__heading">Before a hard fight</h2>
      <ul class="bg3-checklist" data-checklist-id="pre-fight">
        <li>
          <label><input type="checkbox" /> Long rest — full spell slots</label>
        </li>
        <li>
          <label><input type="checkbox" /> Bless + elixirs on frontliners</label>
        </li>
        <li>
          <label><input type="checkbox" /> Greater Invisibility on Astarion (level 5+)</label>
        </li>
        <li>
          <label><input type="checkbox" /> Hold ready — nobody attacks boss until it lands</label>
        </li>
        <li>
          <label><input type="checkbox" /> Scrolls: Command, Misty Step, Counterspell (Act 3)</label>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</details>
